'''2016年貝克峽谷大火'''發生於2016年3月。大火發生於[[亞利桑那州|亞利桑那州]][[道格拉斯_(亞利桑那州)|道格拉斯]]東北部與[[新墨西哥州|新墨西哥州]]西南部之[[貝克峽谷|貝克峽谷]]。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Walton|first1=Elizabeth|title=Baker Canyon Fire increases to 6,200 acres|url=http://www.tucsonnewsnow.com/story/31565816/baker-canyon-fire-increases-to-6200-acres|accessdate=25 March 2016|work=[[KOLD-TV|KOLD]]|date=25 March 2016|archive-date=2016-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160430193304/http://www.tucsonnewsnow.com/story/31565816/baker-canyon-fire-increases-to-6200-acres|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="KNXV">{{cite news|title=Baker Canyon Fire update: Blaze near Douglas grows to 6,800 acres|url=http://www.abc15.com/news/state/baker-canyon-fire-update-blaze-near-douglas-grows-to-6800-acres|accessdate=25 March 2016|work=[[KNXV|KNXV]]|date=25 March 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160407022401/http://www.abc15.com/news/state/baker-canyon-fire-update-blaze-near-douglas-grows-to-6800-acres|archive-date=2016-04-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="Cleveland">{{cite news|last1=Cleveland|first1=Claire|title=Baker Canyon Fire threatens 7 structures, including house|url=http://www.azcentral.com/story/news/local/arizona-breaking/2016/03/25/baker-canyon-fire-threatens-7-structures-including-house/82279292/|accessdate=26 March 2016|work=[[The_Arizona_Republic|The Arizona Republic]]|date=25 March 2016}}</ref>

==救災過程==
現場指揮官為[[J.齊格勒|J.齊格勒]]（'''J. Ziegler'''）。火勢受控後，消防部門派出6架消防車於附近巡邏及戒備<ref>http://inciweb.nwcg.gov/incident/4673/ {{Wayback|url=http://inciweb.nwcg.gov/incident/4673/ |date=20160426081441 }} Information on the fire Incident Overview</ref>。

