大火波及[[新墨西哥州|新墨西哥州]]及[[亞利桑那州|亞利桑那州]]交界的[[科羅納多國家森林公園|科羅納多國家森林公園]]<ref name="Reyes">{{cite news|last1=Reyes|first1=Anthony Victor|title=Baker Canyon Fire grows to 7,980 acres, 90 percent contained|url=http://www.kvoa.com/Clip/12320543/baker-canyon-fire-grows-to-7980-acres-90-percent-contained|accessdate=30 March 2016|work=[[KVOA|KVOA]]|date=28 March 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160423134843/http://www.kvoa.com/Clip/12320543/baker-canyon-fire-grows-to-7980-acres-90-percent-contained|archive-date=2016-04-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

